data-flex-grow="609"
data-flex-basis="1463px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://qiaonpc.github.io/post/digidoc/reading%20files.png"
width="1699"
height="560"
srcset="https://qiaonpc.github.io/post/digidoc/reading%20files_hu9256386855089078482.png 480w, https://qiaonpc.github.io/post/digidoc/reading%20files_hu13014223121907553250.png 1024w"
